{{Infobox language family |name=Yabutian |altname=Jabutian |region=[[Rondônia]], [[Brazil]] |familycolor=American |fam1=[[Macro-Gê languages|Macro-Gê]] |glotto=jabu1249 |glottorefname=Jabuti |child1=''[[Arikapú language|Arikapú]] (Maxubí)'' |child2=''[[Djeoromitxi language|Djeoromitxi]] (Yabutí/Jabotí)'' |map=Jabutian languages.png |mapcaption= }}
The '''Yabutian''' or '''Jabutian languages''' are two similar [[moribund language]]s of Brazil. They are members of the [[Macro-Je]] language family.
